open_spaces_details.open_space_type: Provision for children and young people

description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment to provide 2no. buildings up to seven storeys high plus basement level comprising of 204 residential units (Class C3) and a food store (Class A1) with car and cycle parking, amenity space, refuse and recycling storage and associated access, servicing area, landscaping and boundary treatment (subject to legal agreement dated 4th October 2021)
